#!/bin/bash

cat << 'EOF'
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                     NEOVIM CHEAT SHEET                          ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

NAVIGATION & JUMPING
────────────────────
  gd         Go to definition
  gD         Go to declaration  
  gi         Go to implementation
  gr         Find all references
  K          Show hover documentation
  [d         Previous diagnostic/error
  ]d         Next diagnostic/error

FILE & SEARCH
─────────────
  Space + ff  Find files (fuzzy)
  Space + fg  Live grep (search in files)
  Space + fb  Find buffers
  Space + fh  Help tags
  Space + e   Toggle file explorer

EDITING
───────
  jj         Escape from insert mode (custom)
  gcc        Comment/uncomment line
  gc         Comment/uncomment selection (visual mode)
  Space + rn  Rename symbol
  Space + ca  Code action (fixes/refactors)

COMPLETION (Insert Mode)
────────────────────────
  Ctrl+Space  Trigger completion
  Tab         Next suggestion
  Shift+Tab   Previous suggestion
  Enter       Accept suggestion
  Ctrl+e      Cancel completion

WINDOW MANAGEMENT
─────────────────
  Ctrl+w s    Split horizontally
  Ctrl+w v    Split vertically
  Ctrl+w h/j/k/l  Navigate between splits
  Ctrl+w q    Close current split

MOUSE
─────
  ✓ Enabled - click, scroll, select all work

INSTALLED LANGUAGE SERVERS
──────────────────────────
  • Go (gopls)
  • Python (pyright)
  • TypeScript/JavaScript (tsserver)
  • Rust (rust_analyzer)
  • Lua (lua_ls)

Pro tip: Leader key is Space
EOF